; public-audio-rendezvous.form — public rendezvous plus audio co-presence.
;
; The carrier split is deliberate:
;   - public API / public paste / public archive style pages carry rendezvous cells;
;   - audio proves local physical co-presence through speaker/mic nonce exchange;
;   - oracle calls may teach candidates, but measurements decide what to keep.
;
; FLOOR [MEASURED IN FORM, 2026-06-15]
;   public-audio-rendezvous.fk returns 16383 four-way. The receipt validates:
;     - public rendezvous receipts from coherence-public-api, pastebin-public-page,
;       or archive-org-public-item;
;     - nonce hash visibility, public readability, TTL, write/read timing;
;     - audio co-presence receipts over audio-audible-fsk or audio-near-ultrasonic;
;     - Mac-to-Android, Android-to-Mac, or peer-to-peer direction receipts;
;     - SNR/confidence/latency thresholds and raw-audio-retained = 0;
;     - measured shape cells, recipe steps, tool/reasoning/oracle time, nonzero oracle time, bottleneck,
;       and pressure;
;     - oracle-used as a measured teacher row, not authority.
;
; LIVE CARRIER PROOF [COHERENCE PUBLIC API, 2026-06-15]
;   scripts/public_api_rendezvous_receipt.sh writes a nonce hash as a public
;   runtime event and reads it back from GET /api/runtime/events without auth.
;   Receipt 20260615T152919Z:
;     carrier=coherence-public-api
;     event_id=rt_13fdae655ee1
;     nonce_hash_len=64
;     write_ms=139
;     read_ms=3876
;     ttl_ms=600000
;     public_readable=1
;     raw_nonce_retained=0
;     status=pass
;
; WHAT THIS DOES NOT CLAIM
;   No microphone capture has run in this slice. No Pastebin write or archive.org
;   upload has run in this slice. No raw audio or raw nonce is retained. The
;   public API carrier is live; paste/archive and audio carriers still must
;   return this same receipt shape before they are claimed.
;
; NORTH STAR
;   Each carrier call emits a receipt: shape, recipe, cell count, start/end time,
;   tool duration, reasoning duration, oracle duration, public visibility, local
;   co-presence confidence, and pressure. Once the receipt is Form-native, the
;   body can inspect every segment, find the tight spot, try another carrier or
;   recipe, and keep only what improves measured vitality.
;
; NEXT CARRIER PROOFS
;   1. Audio detection: Mac emits a short FSK/chirp nonce; Android detects it by
;      correlation/FFT and replies; both return SNR/confidence/latency receipts.
;   2. Public fallback services: add pastebin-public-page or archive-org-public-
;      item only as public-read fallback carriers with the same receipt shape.
;   3. Bottleneck learning: compare tool/reasoning/oracle durations and choose
;      the next experiment from the pressure row rather than intuition alone.
;
; KIN
;   device-heartbeat.form, channel-loopback.form, real-mesh-training-carrier.form,
;   tool-channel.form, oracle-catalog.form, code-tool-learning.form,
;   fourth-kernel-wall-groups.form.
